127
00:08:57,790 --> 00:09:01,190
Akulah yang payah.

128
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:04,090
Apa itu tadi?

129
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:06,590
Apa maksudmu Tn. Akitaya, Tn. Otsubo dan Nona Isaka

130
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:09,390
bekerja sama dan membunuh Tn. Hario?

131
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,790
Itu benar.

132
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:16,190
Lalu mereka membuat alibi menggunakan Nona Nojima.

133
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:18,290
Apa kau yakin?

134
